  "body": "### Component\n\nCast\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nToday, to use cast with keystore, we have to add the parameter --password. To be able to migrate from seth, having a password stored on file and pointing to this file using an environment variable would be great and make cast more compatible with .sethrc config:\r\n```\r\n# point to the keystore directory\r\nexport ETH_KEYSTORE=/home/me/.ethereum/keystore\r\n\r\n# point to the password file     ---> [this feature request]\r\nexport ETH_PASSWORD=/home/me/.ethereum/keystore/password-file.txt\r\n```\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
